    "description": "<strong>游戏玩法</strong><br>玩家所扮演的侠客们在游戏中可自由选择初始发展位置，随着游戏进程的推进，游戏世界中会出现邪教毒雾，毒雾会缩小侠客们的安全生存区域。<br>因为安全区域被压缩，侠客们需要获取更多的资源来维持生存，生存物资可以通过在游戏中搜索到或者通过跟其他玩家切磋后获得。<br>如果玩家扮演的侠客在切磋中失败，那么就失去了这场竞技的资格，最终获得胜利的只有一个玩家或者同一个队伍的玩家。<br><strong>游戏特色</strong><br>•<strong>高自由度的玩法</strong>：近战搏击和远程射击玩家可自由切换搭配<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/a82ce59d9a65563efa3c60d362844ad3.poster.avif?t=1588046169\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/a82ce59d9a65563efa3c60d362844ad3.webm?t=1588046169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/a82ce59d9a65563efa3c60d362844ad3.mp4?t=1588046169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>•<strong>丰富多变的武学</strong>：各种武学和心法让玩家自由选择体验<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/ef060db05f428b72526ccb6e06b406cb.poster.avif?t=1588046169\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/ef060db05f428b72526ccb6e06b406cb.webm?t=1588046169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/ef060db05f428b72526ccb6e06b406cb.mp4?t=1588046169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>•<strong>精美的游戏画面</strong>：丰富的动态光影效果烘托出写实的古代世界<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/117c5e7279ed87e969e0d1c8d80ff4d4.poster.avif?t=1588046169\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840140/extras/117c5e727